title: Match-making problems
body:
Hey all,
I'm trying to get into a Classic 5v5 Normal match on the Oceanic server but I can't seem to be able to get into any. I've restarted the search four times and it's constantly not coming up with anything.

Is there a problem at the moment?
Thanks for all your replies!

- Chrono

replies.body:
Hi Chronosima,

Thanks for the report! Can you provide some more details about when this is happening for you? 

What day / time of day did this occur? How long did you wait before cancelling queue?
